{"tid":187333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"埾士提反女生更衣片段被上載雲端分享","createTime":"2017-04-05T00:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T09:20:29.000Z","uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":93,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c7625f423712f28df2de3b9a282c92b6cce32f6","tid":187333,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:56:21.000Z","msg":"百年名校赤柱聖士提反書院驚爆偷拍醜聞，七名男生長期偷拍女生更衣被捕。有學生疑將手機放入學校泳池的女生更衣室偷拍女同學更衣及如廁，更斗膽將片段上載雲端分享，被校方揭發報警。重案組調查後拘捕七名涉嫌與案有關的男學生，發現數十段更衣片段，懷疑偷拍行為維持逾半年時間，估計有不少女生中招。校方昨發表聲明指事態嚴重，對學生違規不端行為感到深切遺憾，涉事學生已停課，受影響學生則獲安排輔導跟進。教育局發言人指，已就事件接觸校方，並提供適切支援。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd2ebc6658677764592b9ab036812eb9623ce8a","tid":187333,"uid":36544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:57:08.000Z","msg":"分享呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135470c177623d4f4a5577d5d3d8c31492b3c0ce","tid":187333,"uid":4301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:57:21.000Z","msg":"片呢？"},{"pid":"eca1ebe8297e7524af834917c16a124d955c4a71","tid":187333,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:57:26.000Z","msg":"隨時兒童色情"},{"pid":"edc54b2266d748481f756c2d7a81c9442e00fd5a","tid":187333,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:59:03.000Z","msg":"點解我中學無膽咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21598824fb801109603c592ea80741a7319ec2cb","tid":187333,"uid":49682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:59:16.000Z","msg":"嗰幾個柒頭咁就玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n抵撚死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 偷拍仆街死"},{"pid":"812aefa9e61313c65f9403983081ccd73505dcdf","tid":187333,